activate(uint256).details: Activate specific beneficiary by index_. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateAll().details: Activate all of beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activeParticipant(uint8).details: Active specific beneficiary by participant onlyOwner

addBeneficiary(address,uint256,uint256,u.details: Add beneficiary to vesting plan by owner.

params.basis_: basis duration for linear vesting. Waring: Convert vesting monthly to duration carefully eg: vesting in 9 months => duration = 8 months = 8 * 30 * 24 * 60 * 60
params.tgeAmount_: an amount of tokens will be vested at tge.
params.totalAmount_: total amount of tokens will be vested.

constructor.details: Sets the value for {token}. This value are immutable: it can only be set once during construction.

crowdFunding(uint8).details: Donator pay ETH/BNB and get quota of token(need donator claim after cliff)

getAllBeneficiaries().details: Get all beneficiaries, only called by owner

getPriceForAmount(uint8,uint256).details: get current price according to the raised amount

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

potentialOwner().details: Returns the address of the current potentialOwner.

releasable(uint256).details: Returns the total releasable amount of tokens for the specific beneficiary by index.

release().details: Release all releasable amount of tokens Emits a {TokensReleased} event.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

revoke(uint256).details: Revoke specific beneficiary by index_. Revoked beneficiaries cannot vest tokens anymore.

setPriceRange(uint8,uint256,uint256,uint.details: add the price for each phase

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updatePriceRange(uint8,uint256,uint256,u.details: update the price for each phase If 1BNB = 1000CPT, the price should be 1000, not 1000 * 1e18!

withdraw(uint256).details: Withdraw revoked tokens out of contract. Withdraw amount of tokens upto revoked amount.
